data.description: Delightfully nestled in the serene settings of Warren County, this split-level single-family home is an epitome of comfort and elegance. Offering a generous floor area after extension of approx. over 2,000 square feet, the house boasts 4 tastefully-appointed bedrooms, including a master suite with a private full bath. An open concept layout connects the living room and kitchen, encouraging gatherings and warm conversations. On the third level, you'll find 3 bedrooms and an additional full bath, providing sufficient space for everyone. The home also includes a versatile bonus room, perfect for a home office or play area. Set on approximately half an acre of land, the house presents ample outdoor space for recreation and relaxation. The home has been meticulously updated with new plumbing, HVAC, and electrical systems, ensuring seamless living with virtually no need for any immediate repairs or maintenance. Schedule your viewing today and experience a home that promises not to disappoint.
